---
---

<section class="escape-hatch">
  <div class="escape-hatch-inner reveal">
    <div class="escape-hatch-content">
      <div class="escape-hatch-label">The Build-It-Yourself Math</div>
      <h2>You could build this yourself.</h2>
      <p>
        It'll take 18 months, $2M+, a DevOps team, a security architect, a
        compliance officer, and an AI engineering team you haven't hired yet.
        And when you're done, you'll have built exactly what already exists —
        except your competitors will have spent those 18 months seeing patients.
      </p>
      <p class="escape-hatch-kicker">
        The companies that chose to build it themselves are the ones getting
        lapped right now. The ones that didn't are already live.
      </p>
      <a href="#cta" class="btn-primary">See how fast you could launch</a>
    </div>
    <div class="escape-hatch-vs">
      <div class="vs-column vs-build">
        <div class="vs-header">Build it yourself</div>
        <ul class="vs-list">
          <li>
            <span class="vs-icon vs-icon-bad">✕</span>
            18+ months to first patient
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="vs-icon vs-icon-bad">✕</span>
            $2M+ in undifferentiated engineering
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="vs-icon vs-icon-bad">✕</span>
            5+ specialized hires before launch
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="vs-icon vs-icon-bad">✕</span>
            Compliance risk you own forever
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="vs-icon vs-icon-bad">✕</span>
            AI roadmap starts at month 24
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="vs-divider">or</div>
      <div class="vs-column vs-patientos">
        <div class="vs-header">PatientOS</div>
        <ul class="vs-list">
          <li>
            <span class="vs-icon vs-icon-good">✓</span>
            Live in weeks, not years
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="vs-icon vs-icon-good">✓</span>
            $0 spent on compliance infrastructure
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="vs-icon vs-icon-good">✓</span>
            No specialized hires required
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="vs-icon vs-icon-good">✓</span>
            HIPAA + SOC 2 from day one
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="vs-icon vs-icon-good">✓</span>
            AI agents running operations on day one
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .escape-hatch {
    padding: 6rem 4rem;
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      rgba(10, 22, 40, 0.95) 0%,
      rgba(17, 29, 51, 0.98) 100%
    );
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
  }

  .escape-hatch-inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .escape-hatch-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--warm-accent);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .escape-hatch-content h2 {
    font-family: "DM Serif Display", serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.6rem);
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .escape-hatch-content p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }

  .escape-hatch-kicker {
    font-size: 0.95rem !important;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55) !important;
    font-style: italic;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--warm-accent);
    padding-left: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem !important;
  }

  /* VS comparison panel */
  .escape-hatch-vs {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0;
    align-items: stretch;
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
  }

  .vs-column {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 2rem 1.75rem;
  }

  .vs-build {
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      rgba(255, 80, 80, 0.06),
      rgba(255, 80, 80, 0.02)
    );
    border-right: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
  }

  .vs-patientos {
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      rgba(62, 232, 181, 0.08),
      rgba(62, 232, 181, 0.03)
    );
  }

  .vs-header {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
  }

  .vs-build .vs-header {
    color: rgba(255, 100, 100, 0.7);
  }

  .vs-patientos .vs-header {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .vs-divider {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 0 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    font-weight: 600;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
    writing-mode: vertical-rl;
    min-width: 2rem;
  }

  .vs-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.85rem;
  }

  .vs-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.45;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .vs-icon {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    min-width: 16px;
    margin-top: 0.1rem;
    font-style: normal;
  }

  .vs-icon-bad {
    color: rgba(255, 100, 100, 0.7);
  }

  .vs-icon-good {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  @media (max-width: 968px) {
    .escape-hatch {
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
    }

    .escape-hatch-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .escape-hatch-vs {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .vs-build {
      border-right: none;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    }

    .vs-divider {
      writing-mode: horizontal-tb;
      padding: 0.5rem;
      min-width: unset;
    }
  }
</style>
